select_columns: CASE WHEN driver.last_policy_id IS NULL THEN '1' ELSE '2' END
CASE WHEN s1.field01 = 'FPL' THEN s1.derived_product_id ELSE driver.master_product_id END
CASE WHEN s1.field01 = 'FPL' THEN sha2('EBGI'|| '~'||CAST(s1.derived_product_id as STRING),256) ELSE sha2('EBGI'||'~'||CAST(driver.master_product_id as STRING),256) END

src_column_name: LEAD(cdc_source_commit_date, 1, to_timestamp('31-12-2099','dd-MM-yyyy') ) OVER (PARTITION BY business_key ORDER BY CAST(coalesce(change_seq,'-1') AS DECIMAL(38,0)))
LEAD(cdc_source_commit_date, 1, to_timestamp('31-12-2099','dd-MM-yyyy') ) OVER (PARTITION BY business_key ORDER BY CAST(coalesce(change_seq,'-1') AS DECIMAL(38,0)))
join_filter_column:
CASE WHEN  driver.cdc_source_commit_date >= s1.cdc_source_commit_date 
	  AND driver.cdc_source_commit_date < s1.next_commit_date
	 THEN 1
	 WHEN driver.cdc_source_commit_date < s1.cdc_source_commit_date 
	  AND driver.next_commit_date > s1.cdc_source_commit_date
	 THEN 1
	 ELSE 0 END
recovery_filter_column: s1.field01 = 'FPL' AND driver.cdc_source_commit_date >= s1.cdc_source_commit_date AND driver.cdc_source_commit_date < s1.next_commit_date

src_column_name: case when dml_ind='D' then null else sec_product_id end

select_columns: case when s1.dml_ind='D' THEN NULL ELSE CASE WHEN s1.field01 = 'FPL' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END END

(select max(p.rate) from (select S2.policy_id, max (S2.rate) as rate from (select * from (select policy_id,case when dml_ind='D' then null else rate end as rate,row_number() over (partition by business_key ORDER BY CAST(coalesce(change_seq,'-1') AS DECIMAL(38,0)) desc) as rnk from glue_catalog.rl_ebgi_gs.tb_t_policy_comm_rate_de S2 ) where rnk=1 ) S2 group by S2.policy_id, S2.rate) p where p.policy_id = driver.policy_id)
